'''Alindao Airport''' {{Airport codes||FEFA}} is an [[airstrip]] serving [[Alindao]], a small town in the [[Basse-Kotto]] prefecture of the [[Central African Republic]]. The runway is {{convert|2|km}} southwest of the town.
The Gbadolite [[VOR-DME]] (Ident: '''BLT''') is located {{convert|44.1|nmi|km|1}} south-southwest of the airstrip.<ref>[http://ourairports.com/navaids/BLT/Gbadolite_VOR-DME_CD/ Gbadolite VOR]</ref>
