{{Infobox television channel | name = DBC News | logofile = DBC News logo.png | logosize = 180px | logocaption = | logoalt = | logo2 = | established = | airdate = | launch = 21 September 2016 | closed date = | picture format = [[MPEG-2]] | share = | share as of = | share source = | network = | owner = Dhaka Bangla Media & Communication Ltd. | parent = | key people = | slogan = | motto = | country = [[Bangladesh]] | language = [[Bengali language|Bengali]] | broadcast area = Bangladesh | affiliates = | headquarters = Ahsan Tower, 76 Bir Uttam A.K Khandakar Sarak, Mohakhali C/A, [[Dhaka]], [[Bangladesh]]. <ref>{{cite web|title= Headquarter of DBC News|url= http://dbcnews.tv}}</ref> | former names = | replaced names = | replaced by names = | sister names = | timeshift names = | web = [http://dbcnews.tv DBC News] | Social serv 1 = | Social chan 1 = [https://www.facebook.com/DBCNews24x7/ Facebook Page] | Social chan 2 = [https://www.linkedin.com/company/dbc/ Linkedin] | Social chan 3 = [https://www.youtube.com/dbcnews24x7/ Youtube Channel] | online serv 1 = DBC News Live | online chan 1 = [http://www.jagobd.com/dbcnews] | sat serv 1 = }}'''Dhaka Bangla Media & Communication Ltd. (DBC News)''' ([[Bengali language|Bengali:]] ডিবিসি নিউজ) is a satellite based 24 hour television news channel in [[Bangladesh]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.prothomalo.com/bangladesh/article/982288/%E0%A6%86%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%B7%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A0%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%95-%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%AE%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AA%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%9A%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%87-%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B2-%E0%A6%A1%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF-%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%9C|title=আনুষ্ঠানিক সম্প্রচারে গেল ডিবিসি নিউজ|work=প্রথম আলো|access-date=2018-07-11|language=bn}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailysangram.com/post/323631-%E0%A6%A1%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AC%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BF-%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%9C-%E0%A6%8F%E0%A6%B0-%E0%A6%9A%E0%A6%BF%E0