The sport of rugby league has seen activity in [[Burundi]], [[Cameroon]], [[Egypt]], [[Rugby league in Kenya|Kenya]], [[Tunisia]], [[Sierra Leone]], [[Libya]], [[Morocco]], [[Democratic Republic of the Congo|Congo]], [[Ghana Rugby League|Ghana]], [[Qatar]], the [[United Arab Emirates]] and [[Ethiopia]].<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.rlif.com/article/8241/rugby-league-continues-to-make-progress-in-africa |title=Rugby league continues to make progress in Africa |publisher=RLIF}}</ref>
